AGM's commitment to 360° Kids

Book an appointment at one of our design centres to sit down with our designer to create your dream basement and receive your design and a detailed quote on the spot.

For this service, we charge a $150 deposit that will be applied as a payment towards your project should you choose to move forward with us.

Should you miss your appointment or need to cancel with us, your deposit will be donated to 360° Kids to help a child in need.
